import { StyleSheet, Text, View,SafeAreaView,TextInput,Image } from 'react-native'
import React from 'react'

export default function LogIn() {
  return (
      <SafeAreaView style={styles.container}>
          <View>
              <Text>Welcome Back</Text>
              <Text>lorem-ipsum-react-native.js is a Node.js and Component.js module for generating passages of lorem ipsum text.</Text>
          </View>
          <View>
              <TextInput placeholder='Username, Emial&Phone Number'></TextInput>
              <TextInput placeholder='Password'></TextInput>
              <Text>Forget Password</Text>
          </View>
          <View>
              <Text>Sign in</Text>
              <Text>Or Sign up With</Text>
          </View>
          <View style={styles.icons}>
              <Image source={require("../ScreenDesign/Google.png")}/>
              <Image source={require("../ScreenDesign/Facbook.png")}/>
              <Image source={require("../ScreenDesign/Group.png")}/>
          </View>


      </SafeAreaView>

  )
}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({})
